","body":"这让我很开心，但我也不能一直把它们穿在身上吧？\n所以，我需要一个人体模特，\n这样就能把衣服装饰在房间里，随时都能看到了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-002-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"这、这样啊……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-002-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"但是，哪里会有人体模特卖呢。\n服装店会有吗？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-002-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"不，那应该只是用来展示服装而已，\n不是卖的吧……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-002-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","b